    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Also sidestepping a cessation of production is Arlington Assembly in Texas, a factory which makes full-size SUVs. Flint Assembly, home to heavy-duty pickups, is also safe for now. A portion of Lansing Grand River Assembly, which makes the "
